ystems-and-freedom-speech&d=m5XrLHEHhhS4xH%2BSicsBHwmr2u8Aa6r9E8tiWteYAjM%3D&h=32fe9f9e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/hong-kong-governments-hard-pressed-national-anthem-law-violates-one-country-two-systems-and-freedom-speech</a><br />\n<br />\n港人強烈希望美國能警告香港警方不能為新武器增加電動槍<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/hong-konger-strongly-hope-usa-can-warning-hong-kong-police-cant-adding-electric-gun-new-武器\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fhong-konger-strongly-hope-usa-can-warning-hong-kong-police-cant-adding-electric-gun-new-%E6%AD%A6%E5%99%A8&d=m5XrLHEHhhS4xH%2BSicsBHwmr2u8Aa6r9E8tiWteYAjM%3D&h=d80cb0cf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/hong-konger-strongly-hope-usa-can-warning-hong-kong-police-cant-adding-electric-gun-new-武器</a><br />\n<br />\n香港普選計劃<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/hong-kong-universal-suffrage-plan\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fhong-kong-universal-suffrage-plan&d=m5XrLHEHhhS4xH%2BSicsBHwmr2u8Aa6r9E8tiWteYAjM%3D&h=ccd9392e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/hong-kong-universal-suffrage-plan</a><br />\n<br />\n《香港人權與民主法》是時候進行評估<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/hong-kong-human-rights-and-democracy-act-time-do-evaluation\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fhong-kong-human-rights-and-democracy-act-time-do-evaluation&d=m5XrLHEHhhS4xH%2BSicsBHwmr2u8Aa6r9E8tiWteYAjM%3D&h=45a6d678\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/hong-kong-human-rights-and-democracy-act-time-do-evaluation</a><br />\n<br />\n強烈反對香港警察。發出批准通知書後，香港警務處仍處於武裝狀態<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/strong-against-hong-kong-police-force-approval-notice-issued